productcatalogservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->frontend\",\n    \"recommendationservice->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"shippingservice->frontend\",\n    \"checkoutservice->paymentservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->emailservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant latency in calls from checkoutservice to productcatalogservice.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"normal_avg_duration: 14931.9ms, anomaly_avg_duration: 27709799.6ms, latency_ratio: ~1856\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Call retries to productcatalogservice resulting in timeout.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Status code '14: timeout' occurred 40 times during faults.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Frontend placed order calls exhibiting error propagation from downstream checkoutservice.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Error 'failed to prepare order: failed to get product' matched in several checkoutservice operations.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n``` \n\nFrom the analysis, an extreme latency issue and timeout error between `checkoutservice` and `productcatalogservice` are apparent. These indicate a probable root cause within `productcatalogservice`. Additional propagated errors and latencies are observed in the dependent operations across services like `frontend` and `checkoutservice`, mainly during placing orders."}
